A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a glowing neon-blue shipping container split open like a puzzle box, revealing intricate circuit boards and holographic development tools floating inside. The container sits on a rain-slicked platform in a futuristic cityscape with towering dark buildings covered in purple and cyan lights. Delicate data streams flow between smaller floating containers orbiting the main one, connected by luminous cables. The interior shows layers upon layers of nested compartments, each containing miniature workspaces with ethereal floating screens and tools. Steam rises from vents below, catching the neon glow. The mood is mysterious and technical, suggesting hidden complexity beneath a simple exterior.
